---
title: Cheesy Potato & Lentil Bake with Crusty Ciabatta
description: This comforting bake uses a rich lentil and veggie mixture as its base, with a golden topping of crisp potatoes and decadent melted cheese. This dinner will keep the cold weather away, but be warned, you'll crave it again and again...
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5cc9167ab675a80015106a8c-60b3831e.jpg
